---
// Home-page story teaser
---
<section id="story" class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-32 border-b rule">
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
    <div class="lg:col-span-5">
      <p class="marker text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase muted">Our philosophy</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight tracking-tight mt-4">
        Great coffee deserves to know where it came from.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Meridian began with a quiet obsession: the conviction that a cup of coffee is a record — of a farm, a hand, a morning, a particular altitude. We roast in small batches, source with patience, and refuse to serve anonymous beans.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[color:var(--color-amber)] hover:text-[color:var(--color-amber-dark)] transition font-medium">
        Read the full story
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:col-span-7">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <article class="surface rule border rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-amber)]">01</span>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] muted">Origin</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Single farms, named growers.</h3>
          <p class="muted leading-relaxed">We buy from cooperatives and estates we've met — the lot on your bag can be traced back to the hill it grew on.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface rule border rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-amber)]">02</span>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] muted">Craft</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Roasted for clarity, not volume.</h3>
          <p class="muted leading-relaxed">Profiles developed for each origin. No two batches share the same curve. The bean decides; we listen.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface rule border rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-amber)]">03</span>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] muted">Ritual</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Coffee as a quiet practice.</h3>
          <p class="muted leading-relaxed">Meridian is made for the morning that belongs only to you. Slow pour, better light, a cup that rewards attention.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="surface rule border rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <span class="font-display text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-amber)]">04</span>
            <span class="uppercase text-[10px] tracking-[0.25em] muted">Trade</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-2">Prices that respect the hand.</h3>
          <p class="muted leading-relaxed">We pay above specialty market for every lot. Transparent premiums, published on every bag at launch.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
